<template>
  <vBasePage :searchOptions="searchOptions" :tableOption="tableOption" @rowBlock="rowClick"></vBasePage>
</template>

<script>
import vBasePage from "../../BasePage/BasePage";
import FileManagerApi from "../webapi/FileManager";
import moment from "moment";
import config from "@/config/index";

var TableUniqueId = "FileId";
var EquipmentType = {
  "1": "采集器枪号",
  "2": "Hubapp手机设备号",
  "3": "服务器设备号"
};
var FileSource = {
  "1": "生产文件",
  "2": "物流文件"
};
export default {
  data() {
    var _ = this;
    return {
      searchOptions: {
        searchOptions: {
          requiredCondition: false
        },
        seleFunc: {
          export: false,
          search: true
        },
        search_controls: [
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "接口名称",
            key: "Url"
          },
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "部署点编号",
            key: "PlaceId"
          },
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "请求IP",
            key: "ClientIp"
          },
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "文件来源",
            key: "EquipmentNumber"
          },
          {
            type: "v_datetime",
            title: "访问开始日期",
            key: "CreateTimeStartDate"
            //defdate: moment(new Date()).add(-1, 'months').format("YYYY-MM-DD")
          },
          {
            type: "v_datetime",
            title: "访问结束日期",
            key: "CreateTimeEndDate"
          }
        ]
      },
      tableOption: {
        tableId: "fileupload",
        tableName: "文件上传管理",
        url: config.pgyerApiUrl + FileManagerApi.GetApiSystemList.options.url,

            field: "url",
            title: "接口名称",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "requestContent",
            title: "请求参数",
            align: "center",
            width: "300px"
          },
          {
            field: "clientIp",
            title: "请求IP",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "token",

            align: "center",
            width: "100px"
          },
          {
            field: "placeId",
            title: "部署点编号",
            align: "center",
          },
          {
            field: "createTime",
            title: "访问时间",
            align: "center",
            formatter: function(val, row) {
              return moment(val).format("YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm");
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    };
  },
  methods: {
    rowClick: function(rowItem, element, baseObject) {
